data.title: Tommy Davidson: On the Strength in N.Y.C. (TV Special 1996)
data.meta_description: Tommy Davidson: On the Strength in N.Y.C.: Directed by Paul Miller. With Tommy Davidson, Christopher Reid. A concert performance by American stand-up comedian Tommy Davidson who jokes about everyday observations in America. This was Tommy Davidson's first concert performance since Tommy Davidson: Illin' in Philly (1991).
